quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Did We not expand for thee thy breast
  94,2,and lift from thee thy burden
  94,3,that weighed heavily upon thy back
  94,4,And did We not elevate thy renown
  94,5,For truly with hardship comes ease
  94,6,Truly with hardship comes ease
  94,7,"So when thou art free, exert thyself"
  94,8,and let thy desire be for thy Lord